<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{% block title %}PDF{% endblock %}</title>
  <style>
    /* reset */
    *
    {
      border: 0; box-sizing: content-box; color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; line-height: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: top;
    }
    /* Général */
    .row { overflow: hidden;}
    .col.col-4 { float: left; width: 33.333%; padding: 0;}
    .row .col:first-child { padding-left: 0 !important; }
    .row .col:last-child { padding-right: 0 !important; }

    body { font-size: 10px; font-family:'GothamNarrow-Book',Arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.4;}

    /* Header */
    .header-simple-wrap { padding-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden;}
    .logo { width: 170px; float: left;}
    .header-wrap { padding-bottom: 10px;}
    .header-bold-title { padding-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;}
    .facturation-block { padding-bottom: 20px;}
    .info-row { padding-bottom: 8px;}

    .clearfix { clear: both;}
    .text { margin-bottom: 10px;}
    .text-mb { margin-bottom: 20px;}
    .text-mb-80 { margin-bottom: 80px;}
    .text-mb-40 { margin-bottom: 40px;}
    .text-phone { margin-bottom: 35px;}
    .text-center { text-align: center;}
    .text-right { text-align: right;}
    small { font-size: 9px; display: block; }
    ul, ol { padding-left: 15px; }
    p { margin-bottom: 10px;}
    i { font-style: italic;}
    sup { position: relative; top: -3px; font-size: 75%;}
    .text-primary { color: #17479e;}
    .text-center { text-align: center;}
    .text-left { text-align: left;}
    .text-uppercase { text-transform: uppercase;}

    .table { border: 1px solid #000; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 5px; width: 100%;}

    a { color: #000; text-decoration: underline;}
    .table { border: 1px solid #000; border-collapse: collapse;}
    .table td, .table th { border: 0.6px solid #1a1a1a; padding: 7px 10px;}
    .table td, .table th { padding: 7px 10px;}
    .table td { text-align: center;}
    .table td.text-left { text-align: left;}
    .table td.text-right { text-align: right; padding-right: 20px;}
    .devis-title { padding-bottom: 10px;}
    .table th { background: #f8f8f8; vertical-align: middle; font-weight: bold;}
    .table-recap-all { background: #d9d9d9;}
    .table-recap-all-mb { margin-bottom: 30px;}
    .img { max-width: 70px; width: 100%; display: block;}

    .w-80 { width: 83%;}
    .text-bold { font-weight: bold;}

    em { font-style: italic }
    s { text-decoration: line-through; }
    ol { margin-left: 15px; }

    /* Legal */
    .pdf-legal-wrap { font-size: 10px}
    .pdf-legal-wrap strong { margin: 0; margin:0; padding: 0;}
    .pdf-legal-wrap p { margin-top:0; margin-bottom: 7px; display: block;}
    .pdf-legal-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px;}
    .devis-info { font-size: 10px; padding-top: 10px;}

    /* Footer */
    .footer-wrap { padding-top: 10px; font-size: 8px; border-top: solid 1px rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.1); }
    .footer-text { padding-top: 10px; color: white;}
    .footer-wrap strong { display: block;}
    .col-10 { float: left; width: 83.33333%; }
    .col-2 { float: left; width: 16.66667%; }
    .col-6 { float: left; width: 49%; }
    .col-8 { float: left; width: 66.66667%; }
    .col-4 { float: left; width: 33.33333%; }
    .col-7 { float: left; width: 58.33333%; }
    .col-5 { float: left; width: 41.66667%; }
    .col-12 { float: left; width: 100%; }
    .text-price { width: 130px;}
    .text-label { float: right; width: 110px; text-align: center; display: block;}
    .footer-page { text-align: right; padding-top: 10px; margin-top: 10px;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  testt
  {#<header class="header-wrap">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-7">
        <div class="col-12">
          <img src="{{ asset('images/logo.png') }}" alt="Muzéo" class="logo">
          <br><br><br><br><br><br>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="information-block">
              <div class="info-row">
                <strong>{{ 'app.label.currency'|trans }} :</strong>
                € (euro)
              </div>
              <div class="info-row">
                <strong>{{ 'app.label.customer'|trans }} :</strong>
                {{ quotation.customer.name }}</div>
              <div class="info-row">
                <strong>{{ 'app.label.date'|trans }} :</strong>
                {{ quotation.date|date('d.m.Y') }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-6">
            <div class="contact-info-block">
              <div class="header-bold-title">{{ 'app.label.contact'|trans }} :</div>
              <div>{{ quotation.user.firstName }}
                {{ quotation.user.lastName }}
              </div>
              <div>{{ quotation.user.email }}</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-5">
        <div class="facturation-block">
          <div class="header-bold-title">{{ 'app.title.address.billing'|trans }} :</div>
          <div>{{ quotation.customer.name }}</div>
          <div>{{ quotation.address }}<br>
            {{ quotation.postalCode }}
            {{ quotation.city }}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="address-block">
          <div class="header-bold-title">{{ 'app.title.address.delivery'|trans }} :</div>
          <div>{{ quotation.customer.name }}</div>
          <div>{{ quotation.deliveryAddress }}<br>
            {{ quotation.deliveryPostalCode }}
            {{ quotation.deliveryCity }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="pdf-table">
    <div class="devis-title">
      <strong>{{ 'app.label.ref_quotation'|trans }} :</strong>
      {{ quotation.id }}
    </div>

    <table class="table">
      <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.chapter_product'|trans|raw }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.reference'|trans }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.dimensions'|trans|raw }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.description_product'|trans|raw }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.price'|trans }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.quantity'|trans }}</th>
        <th>{{ 'app.label.total_price'|trans }}</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>

      <tbody>
      {% for quotationProduct in quotation.quotationProducts %}
        <tr>
          <td>
            <div class="text-uppercase">{{ quotationProduct.chapter }}</div>
          </td>
          <td>
            <div>{{ quotationProduct.reference }}</div>
            <br/>
            {% if  quotationProduct.image %}
              <img src="{{ publicDir ~ asset(image_file(quotationProduct)) }}" alt="" class="img">
            {% endif %}
          </td>
          <td>
            <div>{{ quotationProduct.dimension }}</div>
          </td>
          <td class="text-left">
            {{ quotationProduct.description|nl2br }}
          </td>
          <td>
            {{ (quotationProduct.amount / quotationProduct.quantity)|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }}
            {{ 'app.currency'|trans }}</td>
          <td>{{ quotationProduct.quantity }}</td>
          <td class="text-bold">{{ quotationProduct.amount|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</td>
        </tr>
      {% endfor %}

      <!--  -->
      {% for quotationCost in quotation.quotationCosts if  quotationCost.enabled %}
        <tr>
          <td colspan="3"></td>
          <td class="text-left">{{ quotationCost.name }} </td>
          <td>{{ (quotationCost.price * quotationCost.multiplier)|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</td>
          <td>{{ quotationCost.quantity }}</td>
          <td class="text-bold">{{ quotationCost.totalPrice|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</td>
        </tr>
      {% endfor %}

      </tbody>
    </table>
    <table class="table table-recap-all table-recap-all-mb">
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase w-80">
          <div class="text-label">
            <strong>{{ "app.label.reduction"|trans }}</strong>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price text-bold">{{ quotation.discount|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>

      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase w-80">
          <div class="text-label">
            <strong>{{ 'app.label.total_price'|trans }}</strong>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price text-bold">{{ quotation.amount|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- Récapitulatif -->
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
      <tr>
        <th class="text-left" colspan="2">{{ 'app.label.summary'|trans }}</th>
      </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase w-80">
          <div class="text-label">{{ 'app.label.total_price'|trans }}
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price">{{ quotation.amount|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase">
          <div class="text-label">{{ 'app.label.vat'|trans }} {{ quotation.vat.rate }} %
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price">{{ quotation.vatAmount|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase">
          <div class="text-label">
            <strong>{{ 'app.label.ttc'|trans }}</strong>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price text-bold">{{ quotation.totalPriceTax|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <table class="table table-recap-all">
      <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td class="text-right text-uppercase w-80">
          <div class="text-label">
            <strong>{{ 'app.label.deposit'|trans }}</strong>
          </div>
        </td>
        <td>
          <div class="text-price text-bold">{{ quotation.totalAdvance|number_format(2, '.', ' ') }} €</div>
        </td>
      </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <div class="devis-info">
      DEVIS VALABLE 60 JOURS Le fait de passer commande implique adhésion entière et sans réserve du client aux CGV de Muzeo, en PJ. <br/>
      BANK IDENTIFICATION: IBAN: FR76 1020 7000 9021 2162 4443 752 // BIC (BANK IDENTIFICATION CODE): CCBPFRPPMTG // MUZEO SAS
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="page-break-after: always;"></div>

  <header class="header-simple-wrap">
    <img src="{{ publicDir ~ asset('images/muzeo.png') }}" alt="Muzéo" class="logo">
  </header>
  #}
</body>
</html>
